race.comment: DEALER (7) comes off a (25.85) win last time, scoring by one length in a Grade 1/2 over 461m at this track. Has two wins already from this draw. Rates on top and should go close. WHISKY BARREL (1) was in the placings last time but three back clocked an outstanding 25.88 win over 461m at this track. Expecting another bold showing. BROWSING ABOUT (3) scored (19.58) last time out at this track adding to an already respectable career. Has a strong winning record here. Some good form is emerging from his last run. One of main contenders. LIZZY MILICI (4) was a surprise winner last time, don't underestimate.
